Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八月七日  渚夫人身体不适
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转入了大学医院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来望月女士同样身体欠佳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小瑛一同转院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是忙碌的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八月二十八日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大学医院里  助产医师提及了小瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很有精神  似乎给医师留下了很深的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是从她母亲脖子上拿下的那个挂坠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说小瑛很喜欢它  这让我吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挂坠纪念的应该是渚夫人的孩子  一叶才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想留给我们解决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这本日记带过来后没过多久  她就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奶奶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大夫奶奶  午安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您身体好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好着呢  托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我把这个给带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  这是日记？  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只有一点点  但上面写过一些小瑛的妈妈的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往后她什么都没有说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也没有问她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  你就不在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又能怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去查一查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过DNA鉴定  把这件事弄个水落石出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能答应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她们两个真抱错了  那家伙又会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说渚同学的母亲…就是天女目的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行那我们就换回来吧  可喜可贺可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得事情会这么发展么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世事才没有那么单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙一路努力至今所费的心血  很有可能会被毁于一旦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不惜做到这地步  但你就真的相信能得到回报？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你就真的相信能得到回报？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.54,pos2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}（放学后到音乐教室来）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  你说不要再交往下去  这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  对不起  我觉得我们最终还是只有这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜欢和我交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不喜欢…但是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望自己别喜欢上你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  大家都会不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈把我扔下  不知道去了什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷也把我留了下来  我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再变成孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想再看到珍视的人离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…我不想喜欢上你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算奇怪但却是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有些事物是永远不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里会有…连爱情都会消失不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会有离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！彼此一度喜欢过对方的事实却是永恒的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有永不消失的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我那么珍视的挂坠都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧…怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据最后的结果  说不定连渚同学你的人生都会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但天女目要自己忍受一切  度过剩下的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这实在不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗…就连我自己都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这关系并非真实的话  我也不愿意这样继续生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  渚同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你和那孩子是错领的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  母亲大人还能爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要问这些  你不想做我的女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却有这样的可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性？  这是怎么回事  一叶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有记录说  说不定实情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想做一次DNA鉴定确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事我不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算鉴定了结果还是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果一样也无所谓！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我喜欢瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…如果可以的话  我希望能为她实现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想让我去扮演这个角色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有这么说  只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的鉴定  就是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  为什么我们非得领养她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会连遗产的主意都动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别嚷嚷那么大声  瑛她听得见的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着呢  她到底是个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  为什么要收她作养女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这话算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑛的事情我告诉过你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是听过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩是个没人要的孩子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你胡说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:09:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑛的笑容不会输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的那副笑容  我想为她守护下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴定所需的安排  渚同学已经帮你办妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五天后就会有结果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渚同学说不管结果怎样都不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  天女目你能不能也一起来听听结果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  我会去听的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谁让小一和悠帮我准备得那么周到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日野君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就要出结果了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑛不见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上我打电话想让她一起来  但她却不接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前从来不会有这种情况的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八寻小姐大概是一直喝到今天早上  人没起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一我也问过了照顾瑛的人们但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日野君！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行啊  逃学什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我插足得太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呦喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不是在埋头逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什么结果  大家都会接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我只是个没人要的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没那个意思  也会无意中给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和渚同学从来不觉得这是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然还是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是去确认  梦好像就会完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我多多少少明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去到多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是找不到呢  能够安心的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠？  嗯  送过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  那我去车站
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是结果  瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有人看过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  瑛  勇敢正视现实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我还是不敢看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直…一直从远处看着小一和母亲谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不想破坏这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭  瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小一的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就是你的挂坠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么母亲会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它确确实实是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿起它看看背面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在山里捡到后送过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我还小  看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说  瑛果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来说明当天发生的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小瑛还是一个健康可爱的婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她母亲却没有怎么照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某一天在我一直看着她时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于太可爱于是情不自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  这孩子太活泼了  把我的挂坠扯了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转院之后听说这孩子的母亲已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把挂坠送给这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是谎言  也想给她关于母亲的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之后  我知道了事情的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我一直在回避小瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我知道小瑛是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却还无法敞开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我还不知道我该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时抱着你  觉得你无比可爱也是千真万确
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能够逐渐找回那一份感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  小一的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠  谢谢你帮了不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我考虑过要怎么答谢你  却想不出好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  就让我说一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以抱抱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱抱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  可以再拜托一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后可以每天抱抱一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是也有不能见面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候就用电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  用电话来抱抱  该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说一声「抱抱」就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受一下那心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那就来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也多多指教了  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是  …那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------M---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:53.55,title3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(575,170)\fad(1000,0)}已经第十天了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚实在是万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然丧失了记忆  完全不记得发生过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概给你们添了不少的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请抬起头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然被掀翻被轰飞又被压扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一点也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的是之前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我侥幸胜出  确定初佳小姐一家独败时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起输了麻将的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更像是在一辈子只有一次的恋爱中落败的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.36,0:22:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的话  可以一起去逛夏日祭典吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你去夏日祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和初佳小姐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠什么的最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.35,0:23:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多指教了  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真爱哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.19,0:23:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  在夏日祭典的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终我叫得很尽兴  我觉得叫得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实只是牵牵手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后也没再联络  已经第十天了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.74,0:23:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上为副标题服务的自言自语  结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的总结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:55.97,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,我想叫  让我叫  小杜鹃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待续
